en the rational cohomology ring\nH^*(X)_Q is generated by H^2(X)_Q. Under this assumption the equivariant\ncohomology ring with rational coefficients H^*_T(X,Q) is isomorphic to\nH^*_T(\\del_X,Q), the face ring of the multi-fan \\del_X, and the proof is\ncarried out on H^*_T(\\del_X,Q) by using completely combinatorial terms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2013 00:12:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-13"}
