al case of single-user setup. It is revealed that the peak power\nconstraint imposed on each OFDM SC as well as the number of users in the system\nplay a key role in the rate-energy performance comparison by the two proposed\nschemes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Aug 2013 05:13:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Feb 2014 09:33:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-14"}
